Welcome to my home page!! 

I am pursuing my PhD in Computer Science at the University of California, Irvine.
My thesis topic  is  Power Estimation in High Performance Memory Structures.
Prior to joining the PhD program,  I completed my masters in Microelectronic
Systems from
 Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore,
 and bachelors in ECE from Regional Engineering College (REC),
Warangal (now known as  
National Institure of Technology (NIT), Warangal).

 


Research Interests

  Power Estimation and Design Automation in Embedded Systems
  Low Power Design and Implementation of VLSI circuits
  Computer Architecture
  Design Space Exploration in Embedded Systems  















